trans-unit.source: Contains data associated with a workflow change that occurs during the execution of a workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder data som er knyttet til arbeidsflyten endringer som oppstår under utførelse av en arbeidsflytforekomst.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] When a workflow change occurs during the execution of a workflow instance and a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile> associated with the workflow instance includes a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint> configured for the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent> event, the runtime tracking infrastructure sets <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord.EventArgs%2A> to TrackingWorkflowChangedEventArgs in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord> that it sends to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Når en arbeidsflyt endring oppstår under utførelse av en arbeidsflytforekomst og en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>som er forbundet med arbeidsflyten forekomsten inneholder en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>konfigurert for den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent>hendelsen, kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur angir <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord.EventArgs%2A>til TrackingWorkflowChangedEventArgs i den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord>som sendes til Sporingstjenesten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord.EventArgs%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingWorkflowEvent> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > TrackingWorkflowChangedEventArgs is used only by the runtime tracking service to pass information in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > TrackingWorkflowChangedEventArgs brukes bare av kjøretiden sporing av service til å sende informasjon i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackingRecord>

trans-unit.source: Gets the changes that occurred to the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Henter endringer som er gjort arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: A list of <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.WorkflowChangeAction"></xref> objects that specify the changes that occurred to the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: En liste over <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.WorkflowChangeAction"> </xref> objekter som angir endringer som er gjort arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"></xref> that represents the root activity of the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity"> </xref> som representerer roten aktiviteten til arbeidsflytforekomsten.
